{"tid":1496690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果台灣喺1945年順便獨立會唔會就冇咁多事","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:27:05.000Z","uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f31a445fbcb46c430fd86074c0edbff66c7e148","tid":1496690,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"日治時期台灣喺日本管理下井井有條<br />\n冇乜受戰亂影響<br />\n連45年國民黨第一次踏足台灣都驚訝一個島仔仲先進過大陸(當時支那人連水龍頭都未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n仲有一批精英分子(可惜喺228事件+戒嚴期死得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果45年就獨立<br />\n就唔會有後來228<br />\n<br />\n除左石油冇之外 糧食, 資源都可以自給自足<br />\n有哂立國條件<br />\n有美國扶持援助<br />\n最重要喺有個李光耀咁既天才領袖擺脫國民對支那既大一統思想<br />\n咁支那後期冇可能叫其他國家向一個本來就獨立左同支那冇關既主權國家斷交<br />\n<br />\n以上事件發生既話<br />\n亞洲甚至世界會有咩變化?"},{"pid":"47429c139f4c1ee2c4ed43b83dcfc95706f717ea","tid":1496690,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d68088f8d77399926db9e5a4722b40d81135067","tid":1496690,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"而家即刻同我係電話SET每晩十點<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496636</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnzZ2rL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnzZ2rL.png&h=79e33ac3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n大叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問記性唔好今日十點半先記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都set鬧鐘就唔會唔記得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順手提提身邊朋友！"},{"pid":"cb03983c9eaf2185ec51cf570